<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038479" n="162v"/>
<p> In <rs key="B_1718-07-04_991170517053605501" type="letter">ultima mea epistola</rs>, quam ad Te, Vir Amicissime, dedi die
                    <lb/><date when="1718-07-04">4. hujus mensis</date>, mentem meam libere explicui circa qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stiones <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
                    <lb/>Te mihi propositas, ad quarum aliquas respondi, ad ceteras autem
                    <lb/>respondere distuli, donec vel coram de his rebus Tecum agere lice<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ret, vel distincte qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stionum conditiones sine omni ambiguitate
                    <lb/>in epistolis Tuis mihi exponeres. Quoniam vero hactenus nihil re<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sponsi abs Te accepi, existimo Te ulteriorem de his rebus discepta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tionem velle differre usque ad tempus adventus mei <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetias</rs><subst><add>.</add><del>ubi</del></subst>
                    <lb/>Scripseram quidem me forte sub finem <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>statis <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs> affore,
                    <lb/>sed quia <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Marchio Poleni</rs> jam ab aliquo tempore cum familia
                    <lb/>sua in rus concessit, ut t<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dium solitudinis <subst><del><gap/></del><add>effugia</add></subst>m, tum etiam
                    <lb/>ut certa qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dam negotia <rs key="place_VER-repven" type="place">Venetiis</rs> expediam, jam proxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ma hebdomada ad Vos venire constitui<subst><del>;</del><add>,</add></subst> quapropter Te
                    <lb/><del><gap/></del> enixe rogo, ut mihi significes, an co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>oratio mea in
                    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus Tuis nullum Tibi inco<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odum<del> afferat</del> allatura sit.
                    <lb/>Interim Vale salutatus plurimum ab Adgnato meo <rs key="pers_DE-588-135542472" type="person">Nicolao</rs>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-118509950" type="person">Jacobi</rs> filio, <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> quo nuper <rs type="letter">litteras</rs><note type="comment">Die Korrespondenz zwischen Nic. I B. und Nic. d.J. ist nicht erhalten.</note> habui.</p><closer><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1718-07-27">27. Julij 1718.</date></closer>
</div>
